{"tid":535311,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇睇過Viu TV 日本72 小時？","createTime":"2018-01-20T16:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T11:12:58.000Z","uid":34705,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f473ab4e714395d6115152d6edf0711123822b2","tid":535311,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:50:15.000Z","msg":"個男主持極度冇禮貌同唔專重，喺市集人哋介紹把刀俾佢攞喺手試，佢就鳩up 人哋介紹佢攞住把嘢叫雪飲又殺咗麒麟獸又盛，攞起人哋擺賣嘅公仔喺咁Fing 扮插人，俾個鎚佢學整麻糬，個阿婆烏落去幫佢翻舊粉佢就連續幾次作勢鐘鳩人，嚇到人哋行開埋，去人哋寺廟打座，全部人入晒定佢就笑到縮埋一舊。<br />\n<br />\n你自己都唔鍾意啲蝗蟲落嚟唔守我哋規矩啦，我唔明點解Viu 又會俾啲咁on 9 嘅麻甩佬做主持喎... 請問有冇人知條友咩人嚟？"},{"pid":"579de6112da05af7349899b729c081184cf9b938","tid":535311,"uid":119605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"講到佢咁仆街既<br />\n利申冇睇"},{"pid":"ed6f5121787547483955c57df6cfe06c65073aa5","tid":535311,"uid":110112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/215752_1b9df8a44d8c773a8df1f6e2c96f2c41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F215752_1b9df8a44d8c773a8df1f6e2c96f2c41.png&h=91f86bf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d161c939cbcdd3e18cb925c7fb2d4da151fcd113","tid":535311,"uid":77847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:26:50.000Z","msg":"有睇但focus喺日本啲景度"},{"pid":"de4368d6de42d0b2e9397cbd6a830ada1316b2a3","tid":535311,"uid":87672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"好明顯節目效果黎"},{"pid":"4bdea5770851d51bdc3cf2ba019ee236b68ae0cb","tid":535311,"uid":34705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de4368d6de42d0b2e9397cbd6a830ada1316b2a3","tid":535311,"uid":87672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"好明顯節目效果黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T00:56:59.000Z","msg":"咁佢又真係好成功咁令到我討厭佢嘅...<br />\n但講真，係節目想用討人厭嘅主持製造話題定，定係想我哋睇嘅呢班人覺得佢風趣呢？